lyrics:
[verse]
Pepa got a brand new leather jacket
Rockin' it fresh, he's the main attraction
Stepping on the scene, causing a chain reaction
Got the swagger on lock, no one can match him

[chorus]
Pepa in the house, he's a jacket slayer
Leather so smooth, people stop and stare
He's the king of style, no one can compare
Rockin' that jacket, Pepa's everywhere
